      <p>Any termination by either party to this Agreement shall be given in writing to The Skiff's email address (hello@theskiff.org) or Skiff Mate's email address.<br /> If the Skiff Mate wants to terminate the Agreement they are to provide at least 30 days notice of termination.<br /> Any keys or property of The Skiff are to be returned to the Space within 7 days after effective termination of the Agreement.</p>
      <p>The Skiff may terminate the Agreement for any breach of this Agreement including late payment of sums due by giving 14 days notice of termination in writing to the Skiff Mate at their contact email address. If The Skiff deem the breach to be serious then termination of the Agreement will take immediate effect and the Skiff Mate will be immediately excluded from the Space. </p>
      <h2>22. Change of Contact Details</h2>
      <p>Skiff Mates must notify The Skiff of any change in personal or contact details. If the Skiff Mate has used the Space as a postal or trading address then the Skiff Mate should change this to an alternative address within two weeks of effective termination of the Agreement by either party.</p>
